{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your goal is simple, connect every Receiver node in each level to win. Your only tool: the <strong>SPIN Protocol</strong> itself, which allows you to rotate nodes, altering the signal's flow:</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/about_1.gif?t=1738355406\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But be careful, signals with different colors cannot mix or cross. Sometimes, the direct and most obvious path is not the correct one:</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/about_2.gif?t=1738355406\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For perfectionists, solving a level might not be enough. To earn a perfect score, you must achieve your goal within a time and rotation limit:</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/about_3.gif?t=1738355406\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you progress, you will encounter more complex and intricate circuits, along with new types of nodes with unique and challenging gameplay mechanics. One of them is the Fusion Node, which mixes colors:</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342810/extras/about_4.gif?t=1738355406\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With over 60 levels, each more difficult and complex than the last, <strong>SPIN Protocol</strong> is sure to put your logic and problem-solving skills to the test.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Effortless controls:</strong> Rotate nodes with a single button, fully playable with either a mouse, keyboard or controller.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Over 60 handcrafted levels:</strong> With each new circuit, you'll face new challenges. As you progress and discover new game mechanics, these levels will become more complex and intricate.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Minimalistic  aesthetic:</strong> Immerse yourself in a clean, retro-futuristic visual and audio design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multi-language support</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Steam Achievements</strong></p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Chapter 1 Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3342810/a77aa72193e3a512f2308637a6c505944c8e8a33.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter 2 Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3342810/dad60f740f1fb8b23836282d7195e19f751522d6.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter 3 Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3342810/8d1b253209a25c74b53a0a5ee101872eb47f8238.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter 4 Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3342810/4d5283d792ff2a2bbc15fe65fb6afde9dbdb19b0.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter 5 Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3342810/76bb5aa6070cb73f7fafd3a8b5f16f10b5184632.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter 6 Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3342810/eb5fe2195804941934934da836842f673306ef13.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter 1 Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunit